description: This file defines the interface and function prototypes for the Broadway Web Service Plane (BWSP) Module Container Object, including creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization functions.

methods.name: BwspCreateModuleContainer
methods.description: Creates a new module container with specified context and reserved parameters.

methods.name: BwspMcoCreate
methods.description: Initializes an instance of the module container object.

methods.name: BwspMcoRemove
methods.description: Removes and cleans up the module container object.

methods.name: BwspMcoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls objects into the module container.
